OL,3,CServing police officers urged to have
OL,4,Csay in Everard inquiry
OL,6,FPolice officers and staff are being
OL,7,Furged to have their say in the inquiry
OL,8,Finto the kidnap, rape and murder of
OL,9,FSarah Everard by off-duty police
OL,10,Fofficer Wayne Couzens.
OL,12,FThe Angiolini Inquiry has launched a
OL,13,Fworkforce survey for those serving
OL,14,Facross police forces in England and
OL,15,FWales a year after its first report
OL,16,Frevealed Couzens should never have
OL,17,Fbeen given a job as a police officer.
