OL,3,CServing police officers urged to have
OL,4,Csay in Everard inquiry
OL,6,FIt found chances to stop the sexual
OL,7,Fpredator were repeatedly ignored and
OL,8,Fmissed, and inquiry chairwoman Lady
OL,9,FElish Angiolini warned without a
OL,10,Fradical overhaul of policing practices
OL,11,Fand culture, there is "nothing to stop
OL,12,Fanother Couzens operating in plain
OL,13,Fsight".
OL,15,FThe workforce survey launched on March
OL,16,F31 gives police staff the chance to
OL,17,Fshare their views on issues such as
OL,18,Frecruitment, vetting, culture and
OL,19,Fstandards, including misconduct
OL,20,Fprocesses.
