OL,6,FIt will contribute to part two of the
OL,7,Finquiry, investigating whether there
OL,8,Fis a risk of issues found in part one
OL,9,Ffrom happening again, such as failures
OL,10,Fof police vetting and poor police
OL,11,Finvestigation into reports of sexual
OL,12,Foffences.
OL,14,FIt will also look at police culture
OL,15,Fand address broader concerns around
OL,16,Fwomen's safety in public spaces.
