OL,6,FLady Elish said: "Over the last three
OL,7,Fyears my inquiry has engaged with many
OL,8,Fofficers and staff. I'm always
OL,9,Fencouraged by the commitment to serve
OL,10,Fthe public.
OL,12,F"This survey opens the opportunity for
OL,13,Fall staff and officers to have their
OL,14,Fvoices heard.
OL,16,F"If you're a police constable, a staff
OL,17,Fmember or involved at any level in
OL,18,Fprotecting the public on a day to day
OL,19,Fbasis ` this survey is for you, please
OL,20,Ftake the chance to participate."
